                <h1>Discover the Unique Beauty of Dalmatian Spots</h1>
                <p>Dalmatian spots are a distinctive feature of the Dalmatian breed, characterized by their irregularly shaped black or liver-colored patches on a white coat. These spots begin to develop at birth and continue to evolve as the puppy matures, showcasing a unique pattern that makes each dog one-of-a-kind. Dalmatian spots symbolize individuality and charm.</p>
